 .Cm tablearg
 argument can be used with the following actions:
-.Cm nat, pipe , queue, divert, tee, netgraph, ngtee, fwd, skipto
+.Cm nat, pipe , queue, divert, tee, netgraph, ngtee, fwd, skipto, setfib,
 action parameters:
